text: Ma Xiangjun is an archer from China. She was born on 30 October 1964 in Qingdao. Xiangjun competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics.Ma XiangjunXiangjun MA == References == Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for China
